List of packages to install 


- Qgis and its libraries (gdal, ogr)

- Orfeo Toolbox library (to use it with command lines)

- Anaconda2

- Sen2cor (once anaconda is downloaded)	http://step.esa.int/thirdparties/sen2cor/2.3.1/[L2A-SUM]%20S2-PDGS-MPC-L2A-SUM%20[2.3.0].pdf

-Create an account on PEPS to download the 1C-Sentinel-2 images 
